      "width": 115,
      "height": 160,
      "text": "Replay Engine\n────────────\n500 blocks → ∞\n\n• New block #s\n• Hash = sha256\n  (orig + loop)\n• parentHash ✓\n• Timestamp +12s\n• Reorg injection",
